parameters:
Suspicious Man: "What's the matter, miss... Are you looking for monster
materials?"
Umi: "Yes, but... how did you know?"

Suspicious Man: "Well... you had the look of someone who can't get what
they want because they're short on materials..."
Umi: "You... do you have monster materials?"
Suspicious Man: "Ah... I make my living by selling them."
Umi: "Then... I want you to sell some to me."

Suspicious Man: "Well... if you want to buy, there's a condition. You've
got a nice ass, miss..."

Suspicious Man: "Ah... If you meet my demands, I'll sell to you... if you
respond with that ass of yours..."
Will you accept the suspicious man's proposal?
Umi: (I have no choice... I'll take his offer.)
Umi: "Alright... what do I need to do?"
Suspicious Man: "Well then... please follow me..."

Suspicious Man: "I see... I'm around here occasionally. Call out to me if
you need something."
Suspicious Man: "Oh, young lady... we meet again..."
Suspicious Man: "Hah hah hah... Do you need materials?"

Suspicious Man: "Well then... I shall stock up on a variety of things for
the next time we meet..."
Suspicious Man: "Oh, young lady... this might be fate..."
Umi: "Do you have any good materials?"

Suspicious Man: "Hahaha... don't be in such a hurry... I have some fine
items... However... I might consider it if you listen to a request of mine,
what do you say?"
Will you listen to the suspicious man's request?
Suspicious Man: "Heh heh heh... Then let us begin."
Suspicious Man: "That's unfortunate... perhaps another time..."
Suspicious Man: "Oh, young lady... we meet again..."
Suspicious Man: "Hah hah hah... Do you need materials?"
